01:35:31.646 --> 01:35:32.678
Dá-lhes a morada.

1506
01:35:32.856 --> 01:35:33.886
Já dou.

1507
01:35:34.065 --> 01:35:35.099
Então, dá!

1508
01:35:35.275 --> 01:35:38.062
7100 First Street.

1509
01:35:38.237 --> 01:35:41.024
